Before the executable programs can be built, you must acquire and
build the Xparam library

    http://xparam.sourceforge.net

Place the Xparam header files and compiled static library (xparam.lib)
in the xparam directory before using nmake to build Dirac.

This makefile was tested with the free (as in cost) distribution of
Microsoft C++, which can be downloaded from:

    http://msdn.microsoft.com/visualc/vctoolkit2003/
